00:10:41.940 --> 00:10:44.670
You set it for, say, 30
minutes or 20 minutes.

00:10:44.670 --> 00:10:46.950
You start to work at
your desk, and when

00:10:46.950 --> 00:10:49.270
the timer goes off it's
time to take a break

00:10:49.270 --> 00:10:50.802
or do something else.

00:10:50.802 --> 00:10:52.010
