00:26:39.456 --> 00:26:40.830
And that's actually
what this is.

00:26:40.830 --> 00:26:42.324
Its biofeedback.

00:26:42.324 --> 00:26:43.740
So for anybody
who's not familiar,

00:26:43.740 --> 00:26:45.470
biofeedback is
basically when you

00:26:45.470 --> 00:26:48.670
start to feedback to yourself
one of your own body signals,

00:26:48.670 --> 00:26:51.250
you tend to gain
control over it.

00:26:51.250 --> 00:26:53.767
So that's kind of a weird
thing to say, but in the '70s--

00:26:53.767 --> 00:26:55.600
this is when this
research kind of started--

00:26:55.600 --> 00:26:59.080
they used biofeedback on
college students who would

00:26:59.080 --> 00:27:00.450
come into the research lab.

00:27:00.450 --> 00:27:03.033
So basically what they did was
put a little temperature sensor

00:27:03.033 --> 00:27:05.030
on their finger and tell
these college kids--

00:27:05.030 --> 00:27:06.990
like 19-20-year-olds--
to raise the temperature

00:27:06.990 --> 00:27:10.070
of their finger,
which is impossible.

00:27:10.070 --> 00:27:12.050
How can you do that?

00:27:12.050 --> 00:27:14.860
But it turns out that if you are
actually monitoring that signal

00:27:14.860 --> 00:27:16.390
and you're seeing
it in real time

00:27:16.390 --> 00:27:18.710
or feeling it across
your chest, you actually

00:27:18.710 --> 00:27:22.720
gain the ability over time
to move that signal yourself.

00:27:22.720 --> 00:27:25.660
This is the crux of
biofeedback and why

00:27:25.660 --> 00:27:30.401
this is actually potentially
such a powerful space.

00:27:30.401 --> 00:27:31.900
So eventually what
you're able to do

00:27:31.900 --> 00:27:33.483
is gain conscious
control of something

00:27:33.483 --> 00:27:34.775
was totally unconscious before.

00:27:34.775 --> 00:27:36.149
So in the case of
the finger tip,

00:27:36.149 --> 00:27:38.260
it's the ability to raise
your finger temperature.

00:27:38.260 --> 00:27:38.980
Not that useful.

00:27:38.980 --> 00:27:40.605
Kind of a cool party
trick maybe if you

00:27:40.605 --> 00:27:42.300
