of a signal that's

00:27:44.350 --> 00:27:47.556
correlated with your stress,
with your inner state,

00:27:47.556 --> 00:27:49.180
if you gain control
over that, then you

00:27:49.180 --> 00:27:51.170
gain the ability to
move throughout your day

00:27:51.170 --> 00:27:52.825
and throughout your
world in a way that

00:27:52.825 --> 00:27:55.450
