00:28:10.950 --> 00:28:15.290
biofeedbacked control over
this by kind of feedbacking,

00:28:15.290 --> 00:28:18.455
if that is a word, these
sensors into your own body

00:28:18.455 --> 00:28:21.697
through your sensory
stream and then drop it.

00:28:21.697 --> 00:28:22.780
You won't need it anymore.

00:28:22.780 --> 00:28:23.889
